:

1. *Uzbudljivo* je čekati rezultate ispita. (It's exciting to wait for the exam results.)
2. Ona je *uzbudljivo* pričala o svojoj zemlji. (She was excitedly talking about her country.)
3. *Uzbudljivom* brzinom pokrenuh auto. (I started the car with an exciting speed.)
4. Ona je *uzbudljivim* tonom govorila. (She was speaking with an exciting tone.)
5. Ovo će biti *uzbudljiva* avantura. (This will be an exciting adventure.)